title: 90 Day Fiancé: HEA Strikes Back!
overview: 90 Day Fiancé: HEA Strikes Back! will give the couples the chance to watch and re-experience their journeys in love and marriage, respond to Pillow Talk commentary and offer viewers a look inside their home lives.Couples will also share behind-the-scenes details missed by cameras and address some of the most outrageous moments of the season.Each episode of HEA Strikes Back! will follow the events of Happily Ever After? season five in the same respective air order.
